works.description: It’s Royal Wedding day! To celebrate the big wedding, Goldgenie brings to you the Royal Wedding iPhone collection. The Royal iPhone comes with solid a Platinum rear with VS1 8.50 carat diamond, stunning sapphire bezel, Apple logo embellished sides and buttons with the firm’s London Assay office hallmark and a certified diamond certificate. The Goldgenie 32GB Royal iPhone is available in three versions – Platinum, Gold and Rose gold.
